text: Mushtaq Ahmad Khan is a Pakistani politician who has been a Member of the Senate of Pakistan, since March 2018. ==Political career== Khan was elected to the Senate of Pakistan as a candidate of Jamaat-e-Islami Pakistan on general seat from Khyber Pakhtunkhwa in 2018 Pakistani Senate election. He took oath as Senator on 12 March 2018. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Senate of Pakistan Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Khyber Pakhtunkhwa politicians Category:People from Swabi District
